snippet.title: Boyscout: Patrick's Town - Official Trailer | Latin American Games Showcase
snippet.description:
Meet some of the characters you'll find on your journey, see quests, minigames, and more in this Boyscout: Patrick's Town trailer. In Boyscout: Patrick's Town, go on a new pixelart adventure, playing minigames to help the locals in town while you discover the big mystery underground. 

Boyscout: Patrick's Town will be available on Steam.
